### Generated GraphQL Schema for Custom Group Field

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/graphql/graphql-schema.mdx

This GraphQL code illustrates the schema output generated from a Payload CMS group field configured with an `interfaceName`. It shows a reusable `SharedMeta` type and its reference within a collection's type, demonstrating how custom field configurations translate to structured GraphQL schema definitions.

```graphql
// A top level reusable type will be generated
type SharedMeta {
  title: String
  description: String
}

// And will be referenced inside the generated schema
type Collection1 {
  // ...other fields
  meta: SharedMeta
}
```

