### Configure npm Script for Payload GraphQL Schema Generation with Path Override

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/graphql/graphql-schema.mdx

This JSON snippet for `package.json` defines an npm script to generate the Payload GraphQL schema. It uses `cross-env` to set the `PAYLOAD_CONFIG_PATH` environment variable, ensuring Payload can locate the configuration file correctly, especially when it's not in a default location like a `/src` directory.

```json
{
  "scripts": {
    "generate:graphQLSchema": "cross-env PAYLOAD_CONFIG_PATH=src/payload.config.ts payload-graphql generate:schema"
  }
}
```

